spirit:hwParameter.spirit:prompt: Disable Read when FIFO is Empty
Disable Write when FIFO is Full

spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:script: Enable('PREFETCH', And(Eq('PIPE', 'Only Read Address Pipelined'), Eq('RWIDTH', 'WWIDTH'), Eq('RDEPTH', 'WDEPTH')));\ Enable('AEVAL', Eq('AE_STATIC_EN', '1'));\ Enable('AFVAL', Eq('AF_STATIC_EN', '1'));\ Enable('UNDERFLOW_EN', Eq('ESTOP', '1'));\ Enable('OVERFLOW_EN', Eq('FSTOP', '1'));\ Enable('RWIDTH', Or(Eq('PREFETCH', '1'), Eq('FWFT', '1')));\ Enable('WWIDTH', Or(Eq('PREFETCH', '1'), Eq('FWFT', '1')));\ Enable('ECC', Eq('FAMILY', 'RTG4'));\ Validate('RAM1Kx18 does not support Asynchronous Reads', Or(Neq('CTRL_TYPE', 'Controller with RAM1Kx18 Memory'), Neq('PIPE', 'Asynchronous')));\ Validate('(RDEPTH * RWIDTH) is not equal to (WDEPTH * WWIDTH)', Eq(Mul('RDEPTH', 'RWIDTH'), Mul('WDEPTH', 'WWIDTH')));\ Validate('Almost Full Threshold is not in range', Or(Mul(InRange('2', Sum('AFVAL', '1'), 'WDEPTH'), Eq('AF_STATIC_EN', '1')), Eq('AF_STATIC_EN', '0')));\ Validate('Almost Empty Threshold is not in range', Or(Mul(InRange('2', Sum('AEVAL', '1'), 'RDEPTH'), Eq('AE_STATIC_EN', '1')), Eq('AE_STATIC_EN', '0')));\ Validate('Write clock edge should be same as Read clock edge', Eq('RCLK_EDGE', 'WCLK_EDGE'));\ Validate('Prefetch is not supported for variable aspect ratio', Or(Eq('RWIDTH', 'WWIDTH'), Eq('RDEPTH', 'WDEPTH'), Neq('PREFETCH', '1')));\ Validate('FWFT is not supported for variable aspect ratio', Or(Eq('RWIDTH', 'WWIDTH'), Eq('RDEPTH', 'WDEPTH'), Neq('FWFT', '1')));\

spirit:enumeration.spirit:text: Read Address and Read Data Pipelined

spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:description: CoreFIFO is a fully configurable Soft FIFO controller. It is designed to support SmartFusion2, IGLOO2, RTG4, PolarFire and PolarFireSoC device family.
